  m_Name: Topic_Design
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::TombOfServilii.TopicData
  topicTitle: Architectural Design
  contentText: The tomb is characterized by a concrete core faced with high-quality
    travertine stone blocks. It sits on a large rectangular podium, originally decorated
    with relief carvings, inscriptions, and ornamental friezes typical of classical
    Roman funerary architecture.
  narrationClip: {fileID: 0}
  subtitleText: The tomb is made of a concrete core faced with high-quality travertine
    stone blocks.
